# Approved Image Assets

This repository contains metadata mapping for the approved project image assets. 

> ⚠️ **Important Note on Asset Storage:** No actual image files are stored directly within this repository. To keep the repository lightweight and centralize media management, all high-resolution image assets are housed on Google Drive.

## 🔗 Accessing the Assets

You can access and download all the image files from the official Google Drive folder link below:

👉 **[Google Drive Assets Folder](https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1gSrLcw7klvDDVluANfjT27P-1FA7hJ6n?usp=drive_link)**

Users and students are encouraged to visit the folder and download individual files or sections as needed for documentation, presentations, or development work.

